483
00:27:29.600 --> 00:27:33.600
Imagine being one of those 11 disciples there that day.

484
00:27:33.600 --> 00:27:36.600
I mean it is almost laughable to think

485
00:27:36.600 --> 00:27:40.600
that they were given such an impossible task.

486
00:27:40.600 --> 00:27:44.600
I mean to say that these Galileans of all people

487
00:27:44.600 --> 00:27:48.600
didn't feel prepared for this task ahead of them

488
00:27:48.600 --> 00:27:49.600
would be an understatement.

489
00:27:49.600 --> 00:27:53.600
They must have felt so inadequate.

490
00:27:53.600 --> 00:27:59.600
Us? All nations? Really?

491
00:27:59.600 --> 00:28:01.600
I don't know how you felt in the weeks leading up to this week

492
00:28:01.600 --> 00:28:04.600
but the past few days has been a mix of

