00:28:04.600 --> 00:28:12.600
I must say worship and doubt in my own soul.

494
00:28:12.600 --> 00:28:14.600
It's easy to start looking forward to

495
00:28:14.600 --> 00:28:16.600
everything the Lord is going to do

496
00:28:16.600 --> 00:28:19.600
but also start to look at the wind and the waves

497
00:28:19.600 --> 00:28:21.600
and the logistics of everything that needs to happen

498
00:28:21.600 --> 00:28:24.600
in the coming days and weeks.

499
00:28:24.600 --> 00:28:25.600
Am I the only one who feels that way

500
00:28:25.600 --> 00:28:28.600
or are there other people who feel that too?

501
00:28:28.600 --> 00:28:30.600
